page_title: 'Use the Azure Developer CLI to deploy resources for Azure OpenAI On Your Data'
page_description: Use this article to learn how to automate resource deployment for Azure OpenAI On Your Data.
chunk_content: Connect or create an applicationAfter you run the `azd` template and upload your data, you're ready to start using Azure OpenAI On Your Data. For code samples that you can use to build your applications, see the quickstart article.
